Warm greetings from the Terry Fox Run Organizing team!

Like every year, Terry Fox Run comes back to our institute. The run is
scheduled to be held on *21st August 2016*. As part of organizing the run,
our organizing team is in search of volunteers. All those who are
interested, please fill up the form <https://goo.gl/forms/f9fSzF5BFDEnCZEC3>.
Only the first 60 volunteers who register will be selected for the event.

